## 1) Dashboard (Admin Home)

### What it should show (CEO-level but actionable)

**KPI Cards**

* New Applications (Today / 7 days)
* Pending Review (requires human action)
* Awaiting Documents
* Approved (not disbursed yet)
* Active Loans
* Overdue Payments (count + â‚¦ value)

**Queues Preview**

* â€œNeeds Review Nowâ€ (top 10)
* â€œHigh Riskâ€ (top 10)
* â€œStuck for >48hâ€ (top 10)

**Operational Insights**

* Average decision time
* Approval rate
* Common rejection reasons (top 5)

**Why:** The dashboard tells the credit officer where to start *without thinking*.

