## 8) The Admin UI style (your elegance requirement)

Make admin feel â€œpremium + clearâ€:

* Card layout, soft shadows
* Left navigation with icons
* Consistent badges:

  * Green = good/verified
  * Amber = review/pending
  * Red = high risk/fail
* A lot of whitespace
* A strong typography scale

This is where shadcn/ui + Tailwind + TanStack Table shines (if youâ€™re on React).
